Discover Beachside Performing Arts
At Beachside Performing Arts, we offer a wide variety of classes and programs designed to nurture your musical talents. From musical theatre to private lessons, our flexible schedules accommodate all ages and skill levels. Join us to explore your passion for music in a supportive and inspiring environment.
Musical Theatre Classes
Our musical theatre classes combine acting, singing, and dancing, providing a comprehensive education. Students participate in productions throughout the year.
Learn More
Private Lessons Tailored for You
Our private lessons are customized to meet the individual needs of each student, offering personalized instruction in various instruments and vocal training.
Learn More
Engaging Singing Camps
Our singing camps are designed for students of all ages to improve their vocal skills in a fun and supportive environment, with performance opportunities.
Learn More
Enhance Your Skills with Weekly Instrumental Classes
Join our weekly instrumental classes and unlock your musical potential. Our expert instructors provide personalized guidance, ensuring you master your chosen instrument. Whether you’re a beginner or advanced, our classes cater to all skill levels, fostering growth and confidence.

Master the Violin with Expert Guidance
Our professional violin classes offer personalized instruction from experienced teachers, ensuring each student receives the attention they need to excel. Whether you’re a beginner or refining your skills, our supportive environment fosters growth and confidence.

Unlock Your Musical Potential with Rythm
Join our dynamic rhythm and singing classes designed to enhance your musical skills. Our expert instructors provide personalized guidance, ensuring you gain confidence and proficiency in your musical journey.
